cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image segmentation. It may also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories as these fields often involve image analysis and segmentation. Additionally, the use of clustering algorithms suggests it may belong to the neural networks and learning (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the application of the method to 3D electron microscopic brain images suggests it may also belong to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
